Quis nunc rempublicam nisi spe lucri aut honoris gratia capessit? Quis non ita gerit vt questum facere videatur, vt hostem agat eorum quibus debuerat etiam vite suae dispendio consulere. 23. relicto Louanio] Erasmus’ move- ments cannot be closely followed. About 1 Aug. he was at Louvain (Ep. 1001. 3); e. 7 Aug. at Mechlin (Ep. 1001. 7n); 7—15 Aug. at Antwerp :Epp. 1001-9), and perhaps longer. Later hc was at Bruges (Ep. 1012), where c. 28 Aug. he met Campegio (Ep.

1025. 4n); and there. are indications of a visit to Brussels (Epp. 1040. 1, 1041. 25), which may, however, have been later (see p. 111).
